Azukki,is,a,cloud,based,platform,that,serves,as,a,backend,for,online,games,It,offers,functions,for,the,creation,and,management,of,items,in,game,currencies,and,leaderboards,for,any,metric,and,over,any,timeframe,Azukki,also,provides,a,way,to,keep,players,information,synchronized,when,they,move,between,devices,and,platforms,The,RESTful,Azukki,API,uses,JSON,formatted,calls,and,makes,the,platform,accessible,for,integration